Categories define attack type, monsters are group 1-5 in stats. 

Groups:
* Award (n) XP where n is the group number.
* 50HP + (n-1)25
* If magic, 50MP + (n-1)25
* Stats 8 + (n-1)2
* int used when magic, str used when melee
* Does ((d4*str|int)/6, (d6*str|int)/5, (d8*str|int)/4, (d10*str|int)/3, (d12*str|int/2) per group.

